http://www.bbc.com/earth/story/20141001-predator-x-hunts-in-the-deep
An ancient giant of the deep tracks down its prey
Go hunting in deep water with Predator X (Pliosaurus funkei) where it is able to use its full power, derived from its massive size.Narrated by John Hurt, BBC Earth's Planet Dinosaur tells the stories of the biggest, deadliest and weirdest creatures ever to walk the Earth, using the latest fossil evidence and immersive computer graphics.